amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;武漢&rdquo;號驅逐艦&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AeN8M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAeN8M.jpg&h=097c8577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9時30分左右，今天編隊工作的高潮：武器射擊訓練開始了！這也是我們最感興趣的時刻，<br />\n按照訓練計劃，今天將組織主炮、副炮, 干擾彈以及輕武器的實彈射擊。而拍攝這些新型武器<br />\n裝備的實彈射擊，對於我們來說，無疑有著巨大的誘惑。<br />\n<br />\n目標靶由&quot;微山湖&quot;艦佈放，之後，它就離開編隊，再次返回亞丁灣。它還將在亞丁灣默默<br />\n漂泊4個月。目送它的遠離，我們不免感覺有些悲壯，有些欽佩。<br />\n<br />\n然而，實彈射擊的開局並不順利，當我們守候在&quot;武漢&quot;艦左舷瞭望平台準備拍攝前主炮射擊時，卻遲遲不見炮身旋轉！是不是出了問題？我們的擔心變成了現實：原來，是炮瞄雷達在捕捉目標時，對海面上的兩個相近目標不能自動做出選擇，總是在兩者間跳來跳去，形不成射擊中心。</blockquote><br />\n定遠號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd2dff84cc4f2eb67c1d0e692c1293e95dd163a","tid":315932,"uid":47845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行到咁遠已經有進步</blockquote><br />\n行到已經有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf78f107a3db5607d00dd7d57c17508345a014e","tid":315932,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8e45a586d72ef4142e2cb8261dc41ad4146820","tid":315932,"uid":32721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:04:26.000Z","msg":"唔係即場爆炸算係咁"},{"pid":"b17c48c12d0c3873c37f9d7970b5c4ac76d801bc","tid":315932,"uid":27206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:14:19.000Z","msg":"哎喲喲，陰公豬"},{"pid":"4c610a558e5781cf72c53036e63762437e058bbd","tid":315932,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班五毛呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面有隻，係咁問人證唔證實到<br />\n<br />\n人地樓主都有帖link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /